snippet.title: The Elder Scrolls Online: Gates of Oblivion - Blackwood Expansion Trailer
snippet.description:
Welcome to the Blackwood! A new expansion set within the world of The Elder Scrolls Online, part of the Gates of Oblivion update. Blackwood launches June 1st for PC and Stadia and June 8th for PS4 and Xbox One.

Set 800 years before the events of The Elder Scrolls IV: Oblivion, this expansion will act as a prequel allows players to explore the diverse region of Blackwood. Will you be able to stop Mehrunes Dagon, Daedric Prince of Destruction and save Tamriel?
